mp;protocol=v2&amp;sampling=False&amp;animatedImagePlayCount=1&amp;overTime=60&amp;incremental=False&amp;sceneCode=article_draft_web&amp;animatedImageAutoPlay=False&amp;retryCount=3&amp;precoder=False&amp;draft_token=2047047380986508189\" data-watermark-src=\"https://pic-private.zhihu.com/v2-fbdb537245d9bcc5cecd28065f8f13d4~resize:1440:q75.jpg?source=1f5c5e47&amp;expiration=1780837728&amp;auth_key=1780837728-0-0-0b0aed9095c038cc8543a9d77ef011bf&amp;protocol=v2&amp;sampling=False&amp;animatedImagePlayCount=1&amp;overTime=60&amp;incremental=False&amp;sceneCode=article_draft_web&amp;animatedImageAutoPlay=False&amp;retryCount=3&amp;precoder=False\" data-private-watermark-src=\"\"></p>\n  <p>然后就是一个城市：</p>\n  <p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://pic-out.zhimg.com/v2-d3ff12de18eb7601f02b279d41e1cb55~resize:1440:q75.jpg?animatedImageAutoPlay=false&amp;animatedImagePlayCount=1&amp;auth_key=1780834436-0-0-4574c47382f6cd6eee45f6903b99afc1&amp;bizSceneCode=article_draft&amp;expiration=1780834436&amp;incremental=false&amp;mid=36f69162230003d316d0b8a6d8da20ba&amp;overTime=60&amp;precoder=false&amp;protocol=v2&amp;retryCount=3&amp;sampling=false&amp;sceneCode=editor_copy_outbound&amp;source=bfcaadb1\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"608\" data-watermark=\"original\" data-original-src=\"https://pic-private.zhihu.com/v2-d3ff12de18eb7601f02b279d41e1cb55~resize:0:q75.jpg?source=1f5c5e47&amp;expiration=1780837728&amp;auth_key=1780837728-0-0-2fc1be44d4bb3acc5358bf1abd49f975&amp;protocol=v2&amp;sampling=False&amp;animatedImagePlayCount=1&amp;overTime=60&amp;incremental=False&amp;sceneCode=article_draft_web&amp;animatedImageAutoPlay=False&amp;retryCount=3&amp;precoder=False&amp;draft_token=2047047380986508189\" data-watermark-src=\"https://pic-private.zhihu.com/v2-83fe559bbfd84283da391349df782604~resize:1440:q75.jpg?source=1f5c5e47&amp;expiration=1780837728&amp;auth_key=1780837728-0-0-ac87a5a893260696653cb5a1765ab98c&amp;protocol=v2&amp;sampling=False&amp;animatedImagePlayCount=1&amp;overTime=60&amp;incremental=False&amp;sceneCode=article_draft_web&amp;animatedImageAutoPlay=False&amp;retryCount=3&amp;precoder=False\" data-private-watermark-src=\"\"></p>\n  <p>预想的日常场景长这样：</p>\n  <p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://pic-out.zhimg.com/v2-e20353645932aa1595cea51e7f5df911~resize:1440:q75.jpg?animatedImageAutoPlay=false&amp;animatedImagePlayCount=1&amp;auth_key=1780834436-0-0-42700942b6fe732253320b559f921fb8&amp;bizSceneCode=article_draft&amp;expiration=1780834436&amp;incremental=false&amp;mid=36f69162230003d316d0b8a6d8da20ba&amp;overTime=60&amp;precoder=false&amp;protocol=v2&amp;retryCount=3&amp;sampling=false&amp;sceneCode=editor_copy_outbound&amp;source=bfcaadb1\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"608\" data-watermark=\"original\" data-original-src=\"https://pic-private.zhihu.com/v2-e20353645932aa1595cea51e7f5df911~resize:0:q75.jpg?source=1f5c5e47&amp;expiration=1780837727&amp;auth_key=1780837727-0-0-738a48ca528ea367a358e8a75d1eca6e&amp;protocol=v2&amp;sampling=False&amp;animatedImagePlayCount=1&amp;overTime=60&amp;incremental=False&amp;sceneCode=article_draft_web&amp;animatedImageAutoPlay=False&amp;retryCount=3&amp;precoder=False&amp;draft_token=2047047380986508189\" data-watermark-src=\"https://pic-private.zhihu.com/v2-ce1eac213be7e422819c4498f39b53df~resize:1440:q75.jpg?source=1f5c5e47&amp;expiration=1780837728&amp;auth_key=1780837728-0-0-98ce50410529e32778a56c3234dc66b2&amp;protocol=v2&amp;sampling=False&amp;animatedImagePlayCount=1&amp;overTime=60&amp;incremental=False&amp;sceneCode=article_draft_web&amp;animatedImageAutoPlay=False&amp;retryCount=3&amp;precoder=False\" data-private-watermark-src=\"\"></p>\n  <p>那么最初的补给从哪里来？</p>\n  <p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://pic-out.zhimg.com/v2-6d8676ee832c12c30d4eddba3e9aa031~resize:1440:q75.jpg?animatedImageAutoPlay=false&amp;animatedImagePlayCount=1&amp;auth_key=1780834436-0-0-4f5b6062c93f0e51048669e9bcc203c7&amp;bizSceneCode=article_draft&amp;expiration=1780834436&amp;incremental=false&amp;mid=36f69162230003d316d0b8a6d8da20ba&amp;overTime=60&amp;precoder=false&amp;protocol=v2&amp;retryCount=3&amp;sampling=false&amp;sceneCode=editor_copy_outbound&amp;source=bfcaadb1\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"608\" data-watermark=\"original\" data-original-src=\"https://pic-private.zhihu.com/v2-6d8676ee832c12c30d4eddba3e9aa031~resize:0:q75.jpg?source=1f5c5e47&amp;expiration=1780837728&amp;auth_key=1780837728-0-0-64aaed13f71787e8505b13efdeadc21a&amp;protocol=v2&amp;sampling=False&amp;animatedImagePlayCount=1&amp;overTime=60&amp;incremental=False&amp;sceneCode=article_draft_web&amp;animatedImageAutoPlay=False&amp;retryCount=3&amp;precoder=False&amp;draft_token=2047047380986508189\" data-watermark-src=\"https://pic-private.zhihu.com/v2-a8c2901b89680523a453211fef5c9d01~resize:1440:q75.jpg?source=1f5c5e47&amp;expiration=1780837728&amp;auth_key=1780837728-0-0-a019651e8e2f2760b491cd8b4755263a&amp;protocol=v2&amp;sampling=False&amp;animatedImagePlayCount=1&amp;overTime=60&amp;incremental=False&amp;sceneCode=article_draft_web&amp;animatedImageAutoPlay=False&amp;retryCount=3&amp;precoder=False\" data-private-watermark-src=\"\"></p>\n  <p>地球运输。</p>\n  <p>最后，回到一切的基础——大火箭。</p>\n  <p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://pic-out.zhimg.com/v2-63b11134b23aeb532c86cec7bb852c4c~resize:1440:q75.jpg?animatedImageAutoPlay=false&amp;animatedImagePlayCount=1&amp;auth_key=1780834436-0-0-81c1183bdb7d6290087188e0031a2d7f&amp;bizSceneCode=article_draft&amp;expiration=1780834436&amp;incremental=false&amp;mid=36f69162230003d316d0b8a6d8da20ba&amp;overTime=60&amp;precoder=false&amp;protocol=v2&amp;retryCount=3&amp;sampling=false&amp;sceneCode=editor_copy_outbound&amp;source=bfcaadb1\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"608\" data-watermark=\"original\" data-original-src=\"https://pic-private.zhihu.com/v2-63b11134b23aeb532c86cec7bb852c4c~resize:0:q75.jpg?source=1f5c5e47&amp;expiration=1780837728&amp;auth_key=1780837728-0-0-c7714d170bd1288f9b0ea74a04f21ab4&amp;protocol=v2&amp;sampling=False&amp;animatedImagePlayCount=1&amp;overTime=60&amp;incremental=False&amp;sceneCode=article_draft_web&amp;animatedImageAutoPlay=False&amp;retryCount=3&amp;precoder=False&amp;draft_token=2047047380986508189\" data-watermark-src=\"https://pic-private.zhihu.com/v2-bec7e7907c3dda9227350c6aafbf9d8e~resize:1440:q75.jpg?source=1f5c5e47&amp;expiration=1780837728&amp;auth_key=1780837728-0-0-bb6315fff1d1a6ebade1fc06764654b0&amp;protocol=v2&amp;sampling=False&amp;animatedImagePlayCount=1&amp;overTime=60&amp;incremental=False&amp;sceneCode=article_draft_web&amp;animatedImageAutoPlay=False&amp;retryCount=3&amp;precoder=False\" data-private-watermark-src=\"\"></p>\n  <p>还顺带制作了一段未来感十足的宣传片。</p>\n  <p>但这个宣传片，不是讲“火星殖民生活”，而是为火星计划准备的大火箭，如何先改变地球生活。</p>\n  <p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://pic-out.zhimg.com/v2-2d06edddcf02e8234b3466c890c7dce8~resize:1440:q75.gif?animatedImageAutoPlay=false&amp;animatedImagePlayCount=1&amp;auth_key=1780834436-0-0-0fd6aca83bb91d088e990967c70f996c&amp;bizSceneCode=article_draft&amp;expiration=1780834436&amp;incremental=false&amp;mid=36f69162230003d316d0b8a6d8da20ba&amp;overTime=60&amp;precoder=false&amp;protocol=v2&amp;retryCount=3&amp;sampling=false&amp;sceneCode=editor_copy_outbound&amp;source=bfcaadb1\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"600\" data-rawheight=\"338\" data-watermark=\"original\" data-original-src=\"https://pic-private.zhihu.com/v2-2d06edddcf02e8234b3466c890c7dce8~resize:0:q75.gif?source=1f5c5e47&amp;expiration=1780837728&amp;auth_key=1780837728-0-0-0466ce0542e6e39904d3e029be0a50c2&amp;protocol=v2&amp;sampling=False&amp;animatedImagePlayCount=1&amp;overTime=60&amp;incremental=False&amp;sceneCode=article_draft_web&amp;animatedImageAutoPlay=False&amp;retryCount=3&amp;precoder=False&amp;draft_token=2047047380986508189\" data-watermark-src=\"https://pic-private.zhihu.com/v2-2d06edddcf02e8234b3466c890c7dce8~resize:1440:q75.gif?source=1f5c5e47&amp;expiration=1780837728&amp;auth_key=1780837728-0-0-8bc800199852bc58590b70c5cd642240&amp;protocol=v2&amp;sampling=False&amp;animatedImagePlayCount=1&amp;overTime=60&amp;incremental=False&amp;sceneCode=article_draft_web&amp;animatedImageAutoPlay=False&amp;retryCount=3&amp;precoder=False\" data-private-watermark-src=\"\"></p>\n  <p>火箭可以代替国际飞行，并且大大缩短时间。</p>\n  <p>动不动数十小时的越洋国际航班，用火箭就会大大缩短。</p>\n  <p>比如从纽约登火箭，出发：</p>\n  <p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://pic-out.zhimg.com/v2-800f08d841d7b0596f9e209f2cdb3450~resize:1440:q75.gif?animatedImageAutoPlay=false&amp;animatedImagePlayCount=1&amp;auth_key=1780834436-0-0-bb9f69b58a871d82e1a9ed9be0a21a1d&amp;bizSceneCode=article_draft&amp;expiration=1780834436&amp;incremental=false&amp;mid=36f69162230003d316d0b8a6d8da20ba&amp;overTime=60&amp;precoder=false&amp;protocol=v2&amp;retryCount=3&amp;sampling=false&amp;sceneCode=editor_copy_outbound&amp;source=bfcaadb1\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"600\" data-rawheight=\"338\" data-watermark=\"original\" data-original-src=\"https://pic-private.zhihu.com/v2-800f08d841d7b0596f9e209f2cdb3450~resize:0:q75.gif?source=1f5c5e47&amp;expiration=1780837728&amp;auth_key=1780837728-0-0-2ab2ab66b20e5b32caf8626851cad205&amp;protocol=v2&amp;sampling=False&amp;animatedImagePlayCount=1&amp;overTime=60&amp;incremental=False&amp;sceneCode=article_draft_web&amp;animatedImageAutoPlay=False&amp;retryCount=3&amp;precoder=False&amp;draft_token=2047047380986508189\" data-watermark-src=\"https://pic-private.zhihu.com/v2-800f08d841d7b0596f9e209f2cdb3450~resize:1440:q75.gif?source=1f5c5e47&amp;expiration=1780837728&amp;auth_key=1780837728-0-0-e53c62375d3a51a622e78332e0f9bf8d&amp;protocol=v2&amp;sampling=False&amp;animatedImagePlayCount=1&amp;overTime=60&amp;incremental=False&amp;sceneCode=article_draft_web&amp;animatedImageAutoPlay=False&amp;retryCount=3&amp;precoder=False\" data-private-watermark-src=\"\"></p>\n  <p>升空，到达地球轨道，一级推进器分离、回收：</p>\n  <p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://pic-out.zhimg.com/v2-bc09732228bde3429a3b3c68801c3ffb~resize:1440:q75.gif?animatedImageAutoPlay=false&amp;animatedImagePlayCount=1&amp;auth_key=1780834436-0-0-e691bc64a0010c075a95fc852770f79a&amp;bizSceneCode=article_draft&amp;expiration=1780834436&amp;incremental=false&amp;mid=36f69162230003d316d0b8a6d8da20ba&amp;overTime=60&amp;precoder=false&amp;protocol=v2&amp;retryCount=3&amp;sampling=false&amp;sceneCode=editor_copy_outbound&amp;source=bfcaadb1\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"600\" data-rawheight=\"338\" data-watermark=\"original\" data-original-src=\"https://pic-private.zhihu.com/v2-bc09732228bde3429a3b3c68801c3ffb~resize:0:q75.gif?source=1f5c5e47&amp;expiration=1780837728&amp;auth_key=1780837728-0-0-d35b649ae5af5f2e29fd67c6cc581bea&amp;protocol=v2&amp;sampling=False&amp;animatedImagePlayCount=1&amp;overTime=60&amp;incremental=False&amp;sceneCode=article_draft_web&amp;animatedImageAutoPlay=False&amp;retryCount=3&amp;precoder=False&amp;draft_token=2047047380986508189\" data-watermark-src=\"https://pic-private.zhihu.com/v2-bc09732228bde3429a3b3c68801c3ffb~resize:1440:q75.gif?source=1f5c5e47&amp;expiration=1780837729&amp;auth_key=1780837729-0-0-56b625f98ffeac2fe33b9f3b0fbe051c&amp;protocol=v2&amp;sampling=False&amp;animatedImagePlayCount=1&amp;overTime=60&amp;incremental=False&amp;sceneCode=article_draft_web&amp;animatedImageAutoPlay=False&amp;retryCount=3&amp;precoder=False\" data-private-watermark-src=\"\"></p>\n  <p>绕地飞行，到达目标地，再推进、下降，点火降落上海：</p>\n  <p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-6882bd02291bd24c26d45287db97277d_1440w.gif\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"600\" data-rawheight=\"338\" data-watermark=\"original\" data-original-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-6882bd02291bd24c26d45287db97277d.gif\" data-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-6882bd02291bd24c26d45287db97277d.gif\" data-private-watermark-src=\"\"></p>\n  <p>整个过程，从纽约到上海，上万里程，缩短至39分钟——目前直飞航班需要14小时。</p>\n  <p>宣传片最后，展示雄心，未来地球任意两个城市之间的飞行，“半径”缩短至半小时！</p>\n  <p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://pic-out.zhimg.com/v2-782c3a908914580e31635cac082e7ae0~resize:1440:q75.gif?animatedImageAutoPlay=false&amp;animatedImagePlayCount=1&amp;auth_key=1780834436-0-0-1a8d0898a479a7fdc232bf99ea1fd50d&amp;bizSceneCode=article_draft&amp;expiration=1780834436&amp;incremental=false&amp;mid=36f69162230003d316d0b8a6d8da20ba&amp;overTime=60&amp;precoder=false&amp;protocol=v2&amp;retryCount=3&amp;sampling=false&amp;sceneCode=editor_copy_outbound&amp;source=bfcaadb1\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"600\" data-rawheight=\"338\" data-watermark=\"original\" data-original-src=\"https://pic-private.zhihu.com/v2-782c3a908914580e31635cac082e7ae0~resize:0:q75.gif?source=1f5c5e47&amp;expiration=1780837728&amp;auth_key=1780837728-0-0-3eb26ad526c25765302259e22f8fa566&amp;protocol=v2&amp;sampling=False&amp;animatedImagePlayCount=1&amp;overTime=60&amp;incremental=False&amp;sceneCode=article_draft_web&amp;animatedImageAutoPlay=False&amp;retryCount=3&amp;precoder=False&amp;draft_token=2047047380986508189\" data-watermark-src=\"https://pic-private.zhihu.com/v2-782c3a908914580e31635cac082e7ae0~resize:1440:q75.gif?source=1f5c5e47&amp;expiration=1780837728&amp;auth_key=1780837728-0-0-4f815eea9b56f0a76beed7990a010755&amp;protocol=v2&amp;sampling=False&amp;animatedImagePlayCount=1&amp;overTime=60&amp;incremental=False&amp;sceneCode=article_draft_web&amp;animatedImageAutoPlay=False&amp;retryCount=3&amp;precoder=False\" data-private-watermark-src=\"\"></p>\n  <p>但为什么“火星计划”最后，配的是这样一个地球商用的视频？</p>\n  <p>这自然是马斯克故意为之，也是马斯克一直以来被认为天才的地方。</p>\n  <h2>创新者、发明家，更是商业天才</h2>\n  <p>作为连续成功创业者，马斯克参与创办Zip2和X.com（Paypal）让他获得了自由。</p>\n  <p>然后得以进一步满怀理想主义开启特斯拉、SpaceX等创新公司的不凡历程，并且从第一天起就希望改变世界。</p>\n  <p>但即便财富自由状态下再创业，马斯克也非常“接地气”，他知道公司的第一要务是生存和发展，<b>再伟大的理想，也需要实现商业营收闭环</b>。</p>\n  <p>所以“加速世界向可再生能源转变”的特斯拉，卖车、卖服务和推动电动化两不误。</p>\n  <p>而为火星移民而生的SpaceX，商业路径上也远交近攻，从当前到短期再到长远，一路非常清晰。</p>\n  <p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://pic-out.zhimg.com/v2-bb018000304dcbe0390788261da27876~resize:1440:q75.jpg?animatedImageAutoPlay=false&amp;animatedImagePlayCount=1&amp;auth_key=1780834436-0-0-6d8337e6bea4c11591ae5daf3c3d88b9&amp;bizSceneCode=article_draft&amp;expiration=1780834436&amp;incremental=false&amp;mid=36f69162230003d316d0b8a6d8da20ba&amp;overTime=60&amp;precoder=false&amp;protocol=v2&amp;retryCount=3&amp;sampling=false&amp;sceneCode=editor_copy_outbound&amp;source=bfcaadb1\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"930\" data-rawheight=\"527\" data-watermark=\"original\" data-original-src=\"https://pic-private.zhihu.com/v2-bb018000304dcbe0390788261da27876~resize:0:q75.jpg?source=1f5c5e47&amp;expiration=1780837728&amp;auth_key=1780837728-0-0-1a8e42e5b428ceda7451f9bc0246ca56&amp;protocol=v2&amp;sampling=False&amp;animatedImagePlayCount=1&amp;overTime=60&amp;incremental=False&amp;sceneCode=article_draft_web&amp;animatedImageAutoPlay=False&amp;retryCount=3&amp;precoder=False&amp;draft_token=2047047380986508189\" data-watermark-src=\"https://pic-private.zhihu.com/v2-638ac4ec10729c81808f68722bbb7cb4~resize:1440:q75.jpg?source=1f5c5e47&amp;expiration=1780837728&amp;auth_key=1780837728-0-0-c933635c8302f9e4782869665d7371fc&amp;protocol=v2&amp;sampling=False&amp;animatedImagePlayCount=1&amp;overTime=60&amp;incremental=False&amp;sceneCode=article_draft_web&amp;animatedImageAutoPlay=False&amp;retryCount=3&amp;precoder=False\" data-private-watermark-src=\"\"></p>\n  <p>SpaceX最初靠马斯克注资，但很快就证明自我并承接NASA等国家订单生存发展，而进一步再火星计划之前，还可以用“火箭载人运输”来扩大利润，进一步支撑规模化扩张。</p>\n  <p>再后来是星链，传统航天业务无法支撑起的火星计划，星链来造。</p>\n  <p>这一步堪称马斯克的神来之笔，星链已经成为SpaceX最大的收入来源，资本只要抬头看，就愿意给SpaceX大笔大笔送钱。</p>\n  <p>如今这一步来到了<b>上市</b>。</p>\n  <p>6月12日正式挂牌交易，就是资本市场对马斯克最确切的回应。更准确地说，1.77万亿美元估值是对马斯克火星计划的全力all in。</p>\n  <p>这也是马斯克区别于诸多嘴炮、忽悠和梦想家的核心特质所在，他是创新者、是发明家，是不断想改变世界的理想主义者，但他更是<b>一个坚定务实的企业家、商业天才</b>。</p>\n  <p>星链负责赚钱，星舰负责花钱，而火星负责讲述人类的终极。</p>\n  <p>当然，商业天才也并不是一帆风顺，马斯克之所以是马斯克，与他越挫越勇、永不言败的坚韧密不可分。</p>\n  <p>SpaceX创办于2002年，最初希望用2年时间完成火箭入轨，然后承接商业订单生存发展，但接下来6年里，一炸、二炸，三炸……直至第四次才顺利实现目标。</p>\n  <p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://pic-out.zhimg.com/v2-f9e8a6945529ce8acd4b0151ece61f53~resize:1440:q75.gif?animatedImageAutoPlay=false&amp;animatedImagePlayCount=1&amp;auth_key=1780834436-0-0-230209ff99a4438de717e1e399624083&amp;bizSceneCode=article_draft&amp;expiration=1780834436&amp;incremental=false&amp;mid=36f69162230003d316d0b8a6d8da20ba&amp;overTime=60&amp;precoder=false&amp;protocol=v2&amp;retryCount=3&amp;sampling=false&amp;sceneCode=editor_copy_outbound&amp;source=bfcaadb1\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"639\" data-rawheight=\"342\" data-watermark=\"original\" data-original-src=\"https://pic-private.zhihu.com/v2-f9e8a6945529ce8acd4b0151ece61f53~resize:0:q75.gif?source=1f5c5e47&amp;expiration=1780837728&amp;auth_key=1780837728-0-0-8af544e01c4e90094ab1b25321832f83&amp;protocol=v2&amp;sampling=False&amp;animatedImagePlayCount=1&amp;overTime=60&amp;incremental=False&amp;sceneCode=article_draft_web&amp;animatedImageAutoPlay=False&amp;retryCount=3&amp;precoder=False&amp;draft_token=2047047380986508189\" data-watermark-src=\"https://pic-private.zhihu.com/v2-f9e8a6945529ce8acd4b0151ece61f53~resize:1440:q75.gif?source=1f5c5e47&amp;expiration=1780837728&amp;auth_key=1780837728-0-0-2be52e871aae01e1bdddf8e220a328e2&amp;protocol=v2&amp;sampling=False&amp;animatedImagePlayCount=1&amp;overTime=60&amp;incremental=False&amp;sceneCode=article_draft_web&amp;animatedImageAutoPlay=False&amp;retryCount=3&amp;precoder=False\" data-private-watermark-src=\"\"></p>\n  <p>并且回过头来看，第四次绝地逢生的2008年，马斯克因创业获得的2亿美元个人财富，基本已因特斯拉和SpaceX投入而花光。</p>\n  <p>当年年底，如果不是第四次发射成功获得NASA订单和借贷款，SpaceX和特斯拉都会破产。</p>\n  <p>其后，为了降低成本，真正做到发射火箭可回收，马斯克的火箭炸了一次又一次，又一次又一次濒临绝境。</p>\n  <p>但最终都凤凰涅槃、起死回生。</p>\n  <p>这或许有运气的成分，但一定也是天道酬勤， 拿中国古语来说就是<b>“天将降大任于斯人也，必先苦其心志……”</b></p>\n  <p>重要的是再苦再难再绝望，马斯克从不说“就这样吧”。</p>\n  <p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://pic-out.zhimg.com/v2-785f61d329103d532196e085ec880127~resize:1440:q75.jpg?animatedImageAutoPlay=false&amp;animatedImagePlayCount=1&amp;auth_key=1780834436-0-0-a4e009d045773e0b589bae03b767e546&amp;bizSceneCode=article_draft&amp;expiration=1780834436&amp;incremental=false&amp;mid=36f69162230003d316d0b8a6d8da20ba&amp;overTime=60&amp;precoder=false&amp;protocol=v2&amp;retryCount=3&amp;sampling=false&amp;sceneCode=editor_copy_outbound&amp;source=bfcaadb1\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"608\" data-watermark=\"original\" data-original-src=\"https://pic-private.zhihu.com/v2-785f61d329103d532196e085ec880127~resize:0:q75.jpg?source=1f5c5e47&amp;expiration=1780837728&amp;auth_key=1780837728-0-0-25717c09038e8c34f7fa7c7e4bf63a89&amp;protocol=v2&amp;sampling=False&amp;animatedImagePlayCount=1&amp;overTime=60&amp;incremental=False&amp;sceneCode=article_draft_web&amp;animatedImageAutoPlay=False&amp;retryCount=3&amp;precoder=False&amp;draft_token=2047047380986508189\" data-watermark-src=\"https://pic-private.zhihu.com/v2-a559ad1429a0540ccdc8ed8ed483d0c4~resize:1440:q75.jpg?source=1f5c5e47&amp;expiration=1780837728&amp;auth_key=1780837728-0-0-1c2cc543b40c02ff58b300053df34b92&amp;protocol=v2&amp;sampling=False&amp;animatedImagePlayCount=1&amp;overTime=60&amp;incremental=False&amp;sceneCode=article_draft_web&amp;animatedImageAutoPlay=False&amp;retryCount=3&amp;precoder=False\" data-private-watermark-src=\"\"></p>\n  <p>他也脆弱、也无助，也被一次次失败打击得灰头土脸，但总是一次次总结经验、再出发，希望再来一次。</p>\n  <p>正如2006年3月，SpaceX第一次满受期待的发射失败后，马斯克在总结中写道：</p>\n  <blockquote>\n   <p>无论上天入地，不成功誓不罢休。</p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p>参考链接：\n   <br>\n   [1]https://www.reuters.com/legal/government/spacex-sets-135-price-blockbuster-ipo-upending-wall-street-convention-2026-06-03/\n   <br>\n   [2]https://www.sec.gov/Archives/edgar/data/1181412/000162828026040364/spaceexplorationtechnologib.htm</p>\n  <!--版权声明-->\n </body>\n</html>",
